headline: Salesforce earnings, September PCE, auto sales: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Jared Blikre previews several of the biggest stories to come throughout next week, including earnings results from companies like Salesforce (CRM), Macy's (M), and Hewlett Packard Enterprise (HPE); the release of September's long-delayed PCE index (Personal Consumption Expenditures), the Federal Reserve's preferred inflation gauge; and the latest reading of auto sales. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.
